Shareholder Name: Abdul Aziz Saleh Soliman Al Amry
Ibtisam Mohamed Abdul Rahman Al Zamil

Description: Jazan Energy and Development Co (known as: JAZADCO) is a public company, listed on Saudi Stock Exchange “Tadawul” (TDWL) since November 1993. JAZADCO operates within the Food, Beverage and Tobacco sector focusing on Agricultural Products. It has 6 subsidiaries operating across United Kingdom, Saudi Arabia, Turkey and Greece. JAZADCO is based in Jizan, Saudi Arabia and was established in August 1993.
